includeit(packages)


Administrivia:
--------------

Information about the various OpenBSD mailing list and proper netiquette
is available at

	http://FabBSD.org/lists.html

To report bugs, use the 'sendbug' command shipped with FabBSD, and fill
in as much information about the problem as you can.  Good bug reports
{:-include-:} lots of details.  Additionally, bug reports can be sent
by mail to:

	bugs@FabBSD.org

Use of 'sendbug' is encouraged, however, because bugs reported with it
are entered into the FabBSD bugs database, and thus can't slip through
the cracks.

As a favor, please avoid mailing huge documents or files to the
mailing lists.  Instead, put the material you would have sent up
for FTP somewhere, then mail the appropriate list about it, or, if
you'd rather not do that, mail the list saying you'll send the data
to those who want it.
